4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals aspiring to become cybersecurity specialists, requiring no prior knowledge. The program lasts 16 weeks and includes three live online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 16 students. Participants gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration while mastering cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The bootcamp prepares students to manage risks through data loss prevention strategies and navigate compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, students receive an official recognition certificate. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop